# Campaign Data (Personal/Runtime)
# Default: ignore everything under world-state/ — live session state is private.
# Exception: the minimal bootstrap files for the Merdo saga travel with the
# repo so a fresh clone is immediately runnable. Live state (session-log.md,
# consequences/, NPC state, etc.) stays local-only.
world-state/campaigns/*
!world-state/campaigns/.gitkeep
!world-state/campaigns/one-piece-adventure/
world-state/campaigns/one-piece-adventure/*
!world-state/campaigns/one-piece-adventure/campaign-overview.json
!world-state/campaigns/one-piece-adventure/bible-sources.txt
!world-state/campaigns/one-piece-adventure/CAMPAIGN_BIBLE.md
!world-state/campaigns/one-piece-adventure/CREW_RUNTIME.md
!world-state/campaigns/one-piece-adventure/ACTIVE_PLANTS.md
!world-state/campaigns/one-piece-adventure/chekhov-rack.json

# Source Material (User-provided documents for import)
source-material/*
!source-material/.gitkeep

